parameters: I have been following Maria for 18 days
There’s no sign of the journal!!
But…Is the journal even the way to go home??
Pa! What are you doing here?
Why are you still here, outside this late
Maria? That should be my question to you!
Why are you still outside? It’s evening
Oh, Sorry pa. I was working on a
school project at school and I didn’t notice the time.
[ I can’t let them know I was with Carlos again ]
Also, why do you look so worried?
I just need some water. Come on let’s go home.
Carlos? Who– Is he– Nevermind that.
Come on, think of our family’s safety first.
…Come on, we have to keep moving
We are in need of your help. It also seems
like they have been requisitioning large houses in the area for their officers.
Alright, where do you need me?
It’s ok ayat… You, promise me you will protect my family
What about us? We need you!
Somewhere far to protect everyone sweetie. Come on, let’s keep on moving.
in our area—we need everyone to lea—
Ayat? Nak? What are you doing out here? You need to leave—now.
Where are your sisters? Are you all okay?
Okay…? Nothing is okay, Alfonso. Lena and Myra are gone…
Wha—what? Maria, where are your sisters?
Tell me this is not true…
Pa… where were you? We… we needed you…
We still have Maria, but what do we do about our two children,
Alfonso? Huh? This was never supposed to happen…
Pa… Everyone's gone… I wasn’t able to say goodbye
to any of them… or to tell them I loved them…
Your sorries won't do anything, you can’t undo the things
that happened! They’re gone, you chose to leave, and now
they’re gone!!! My Lena, Myra, they’re gone…
I should have been here, I’m really—
BUT YOU WEREN’T, YOU WEREN’T AND LOOK WHAT HAPPENED. YOU WERE
SUPPOSED TO PROTECT US! OUT OF ALL THE PEOPLE YOU’D SACRIFICE
YOUR LIFE TO PROTECT… YOU FORGOT ABOUT THE MOST IMPORTANT PEOPLE
YOU SHOULD HAVE PROTECTED, YOUR FAMILY
You’ve been through a lot… only at the age of 14
